OF TALISE DE CULEBRA HOMEOWNERS ASSOCIATION, INC.
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF BEXAR
000 000
"Notice is hereby given that there exists a lien for unpaid maintenance assessments assessed by TALISE DE CULEBRA
HOMEOWNERS ASSOCIATION, INC ., for non-payment by the owner of the subject property and such maintenance assessments
being in accordance with the Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions for Talise De Culebra Subdivision, Unit-1,
as recorded in Volume 15715, Page 1371 et seq. of the Official Public Records of Bexar County, Texas. The property subject to
this Affidavit is as follows, to-wit:

Lot 17, in Block 164, of New City block 18296, Talise de Culebra Unit-1, an
addition to the City of San Antonio Bexar County, Texas, according to the map or
plat thereof recorded in/under Volume 9641, Pages 12-13, Deed and Plat Records,
Bexar County, Texas.
Desmond Mitchell
7911 Cenote Drive, San Antonio, Texas 78254
$1,729.25

which shall be automatically added to the lien amount.
